-create git repo first
-make sure you are on the git repo dir
-use python virtual env
-install dbt-snowflake rather than dbt

-setup python: 
  pip install virtualenv
  virtualenv venv
  venv\scripts\activate

-setup dbt-snowflake:
  pip install dbt-snowflake

- make a dir .bdt in the dbt dir
  mkdir %userprofile%\.dbt
- initialise dbt project
  dbt init project_name
